Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty for everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Angel bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mister Picky-pants, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Carrots, lettuce and apples, yum yum yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what will you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I can even make that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want you to starve...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure I can't tempt you\Nwith a nice crisp piece of--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make your special recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 2 | Episode 19\NPutting Your Hoof Down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed and Synced by GrayJeager\NGrayJeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see.\NAsparagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... I think you just\Nstepped in front of me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I think you made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see I was actually here first and--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, didn't notice you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you just cut in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A cut of celery?\NBut, this is the asparagus stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I think you just cut\Nin front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No need, dearie, I'm already in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind moving back?\NYou're in my personal space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, do you need\Nyour asparagus so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. There's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't let them treat you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really no big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bigger than big, it's double big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a pony with a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead Pinkie Pie, you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there! That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to stop being such a doormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A doormat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A pushover, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to stand up for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,mister small and handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony ever called you handsome before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a big no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well they should!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How about flexing\Nsome of your muscles for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think a strong, handsome stallion\Nsuch as yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,could give my friend the last asparagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's not so hard, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then! What else is on your list?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I also need tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be two bits. Not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But last week it was only one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was then, this is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna argue about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mindin' my own business,\Nmaybe you should try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bits for tomatoes is outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One bit is the right price.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I say it's two bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two bits!\N- One bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two bits!\N- One bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two bits!\N- One bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I insist, it's two bits or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One bit and that's my final offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have it your way, one bit it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Asserting yourself can be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Fluttershy,\Ndo you feel like giving it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I need that cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I glad you have one cherry left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm making this special meal\Nfor my bunny Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a very picky eater,\Nand the recipe calls for a cherry on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you say you need\Nthis cherry very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I'm desperate for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'll be ten bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, mister handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you wanna do the right thing,\Nbecause you're handsome and strong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and big, handsome, strong guys\Nare always nice to everypony, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten bits for the cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten bits for one cherry's outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I insist on paying you... eleven bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven bits?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, nine bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, twelve bits,\Nbut that's my final offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's twelve bits, take it or leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give him your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One cherry is not worth twelve bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I was only doing what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a valiant effort,\Nbut you should refuse to give him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your business and just walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I can't let Angel starve!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't eat it unless\NI make it just right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I need that cherry\Nno matter what it costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, twenty bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty?!\NOh, but I don't have that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why're you wasting my time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you two bits for that cherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a break, kid.\NNext time, don't be such a doormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry there's no cherry on top,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but the rest of it is exactly\Nwhat you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me... I really am a doormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The incredible Iron Will
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,turns doormats into dynamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Assertiveness seminar today,\Nhedge maze centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As Celestia is my witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna be a pushover again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, friends! My name is Iron Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And today is the first day\Nof your new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna hear you stomp\Nif you're tired of being a pushover!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stomp if you're tired of being a doormat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stomp if you wanna pay nothing\Nfor this seminar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no joke, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will is so confident that you will be\None hundred percent satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with Iron Will's assertiveness techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you are not one hundred percent\Nsatisfied, you... pay... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I pity the fool who doubts\NIron Will's methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't doubt me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, no sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That, my friends, is your first lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't be shy, look 'em in the eye."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to demonstrate that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will's techniques\Nwill work for anypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need a volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You, in the back row!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you! Iron Will wants you onstage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, politely walk around him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gingerly tip-toe around him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back home, and try again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"When somepony tries to block,\Nshow them that you rock!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Never apologize, when you can criticize."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, get out of the way before...\NI bump into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You see my friends!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If my techniques can work\Nfor this shy, little pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then they can work for anypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel ready to "attack the day",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as Iron Will says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Greenhooves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think you might be\Nover-watering my petunias...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the professional handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Treat me like a pushover,\Nand you'll get the once over."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that is enough water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Showpony business is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, try one of your jokes out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I laugh at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A donkey and a mule\Nare stuck on a desert island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind moving your carts,\Nso I can pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, in a minute,\NI just wanna finish up this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the donkey says to the mule--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you move, you're blocking my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, in a minute!\NSo the donkey says to the mule...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"When somepony tries to block,\Nshow them that you rock!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy does it, lady. We're moving, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's next, please, and what
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,can I get for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I guess maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maybe"?\N"Maybes are for babies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go to the back of the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,where you belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attitude is so feisty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that monster's workshop\Nreally paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will's not a monster, he's a minotaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And a true inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His techniques really work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they've certainly made a difference\Nin the way you carry yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are a whole new Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.\NAnd new Fluttershy feels pretty stoked
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,about new Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, old Pinkie Pie feels\Nreally proud of new Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Proud as pink punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"You laugh at me, I wrath at you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cut in line, I'll take what's mine!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony pushes new Fluttershy around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,NOPONY!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Pinkie Pie is not so sure
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,new Fluttershy is such\Na good idea after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Rarity agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You got this, new Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This day is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And nopony's gonna take it away from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He's delivered\Nthe wrong mail, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And new Fluttershy does not want\Nthe wrong mail delivered to her cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I mix them up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"You apologize, I penalize!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, do you know how\Nto get to the Ponyville tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, you just--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"You make me lose, I blow my fuse!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no way to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see what he did to new Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And he thought new Fluttershy was a pushover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sweetie, he didn't.\NWe saw the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We think that you've taken\Nyour assertiveness training
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want new Fluttershy\Nto be a doormat like old Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But old Fluttershy is GONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,New Fluttershy... old Fluttershy...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to nice Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We want that Fluttershy back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you want wimp Fluttershy.\NYou want pushover Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You want do-anything-to-her\Nand-she-won't-complain Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many Fluttershies to keep track of!\NMake it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Things getting too complicated for\Nyour simple little brain, Pinkie Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not let things descend\Ninto petty insults!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? I thought "petty"\Nwas what you're all about, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With your "petty" concerns about fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, leave her alone!\NFashion is her passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and what are you passionate about?\NBirthday cake? Party hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that the two most\Nfrivolous ponies in Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,are trying to tell new Fluttershy\Nhow to live her life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when they are throwing their own lives\Naway on pointless pursuits,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that nopony else gives\Na flying feather about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like nasty Fluttershy\Nis here to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe what that monster,\NIron Will, has done to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will's not a monster, he's a minotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Pinkie Pie, and Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! Go away before\Nnasty Fluttershy strikes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweetie,\Nwe all said things that we regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie's right. I'm the only one to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, I'm never\Ncoming out of my house again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony will be a lot safer with me\Nand my mean mouth locked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie doesn't blame you,\Nnor do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You just received some bad advice\Nfrom that Iron Will character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's the one that\Nmade you act super-duper nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there are other ways to assert yourself\Nbesides yelling at everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stand up for yourself\Nwithout being unpleasant about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too far gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I try to assert myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I become a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweetie, you're not a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will's my name,\Ntraining ponies is my game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What a darling little catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend Fluttershy loved\NIron Will's catchphrases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Word on the street is that\Nshe doesn't take no duff from nopony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Iron Will is here\Nto collect Iron Will's fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's in no shape\Nto deal with that creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure a big, brave,\Npowerful and rich monster--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, minotaur, like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't need that money right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can afford to come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?\NFluttershy is overdue as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will collects now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not even sure\NFluttershy is home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be off frolicking\Nwith some woodland creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give us some time\Nto track her down for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will does have some\Ngrocery shopping to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will will come back this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's only half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We need one full day at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will will delay for half a day\Nand no longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A full day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Half day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Full day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Half day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Half day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Full day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We need half a day and no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get a full day and no less!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okie dokie. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like the search\Nwon't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Will collects now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But we had an agreement!\NYou gotta come back tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"When somepony tries to block,\Nshow them that you rock!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your payment is overdue, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were nothing but a doormat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And Iron Will turned you into a lean,\Nmean, assertive machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pay Iron Will what you owe Iron Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to be you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Iron Will is gonna\Nrain down a world of hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,unless Iron Will gets his money pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall, during your workshop,\Nyou promised
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,one hundred percent satisfaction guaranteed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or you pay nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you're not satisfied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony has always been satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I guess I'm the first then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I'm not satisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not\Njust a little bit satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because maybe... we could, cut a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're both reasonable creatures,\Naren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but no means no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No means no, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony's ever said that to me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta remember that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good catchphrase\Nfor my next workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally stood up to that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you didn't change at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the same old Fluttershy\Nthat we've always loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The one we missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Nold Fluttershy's back for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I took the whole\Nassertiveness thing too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Princess Celestia,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes it can be hard for a shy pony\Nlike me to stand up for myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when I first tried it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't like the pony I became.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've learned that standing up\Nfor yourself isn't the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as changing who you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I know how to put my hoof down,\Nwithout being unpleasant, or mean.{\i0}
